Your case appointment with <%= @user_target.name %> is now booked for <%= @event.datetime.strftime("%A %e %B at %I:%M%p") %> 
=============================================

You'll be sent an email to remind you about the appointment 2 hours before it starts.

<%- unless @event.book_id_partnertoprepare.blank? %>
  <%= @user_target.first_name %> has been sent the case that you have asked them to prepare via email:

  <%= @book_partnertoprepare.author.split(' ')[0] + " - " + @book_partnertoprepare.title %>
<%- else %>
  You have not asked <%= @user_target.first_name %> to prepare a case for you. If you would like them to prepare one, use the link below to choose a case:

  ::Choose case for event link::
<%- end %>

<%= @user_target.first_name %> has been asked to choose a case for you to prepare - you will be notified of this via email if/when they do.

If you're ready to start the case now, you can call <%= @user_target.first_name %> using the button below
  
<%= 
  link_to "skype:#{@user_target.skype}?call", "data-original-title"=>"Call #{@user_target.first_name} on Skype" do
    image_tag "https://www.casenexus.com/assets/icons/skype_button.png"
    "Call #{@user_target.first_name} now"
  end
%>

And if you want to start as the interviewer now, use this button to go to the case console, where you can select a case to give, and fill out a feedback form for <%= @user_target.first_name %>:

<%= 
  link_to "https://www.casenexus.com/console?friend_id=" + @event.partner.id.to_s do
    "Start case now as Interviewer"
  end
%>

To see the appointment, use the link below

<%= @url %>